Publication
------------
Pulling Open Doors and Drawers: Coordinating an Omni-directional Base and a
Compliant Arm with Equilibrium Point Control. 

Advait Jain and Charles C. Kemp.
IEEE International Conference on Robotics and Automation (ICRA), 2010.

Python Code
-----------
The code is organized as a ROS-package. All the python code is in the
src/2010_icra_epc_pull folder.


Notes
-----
To actually run on the robot, this code requires some robot specific
control code. Please email the author if you are interested in
looking at or using the robot specific code.




